#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.groupby.DataFrameGroupBy.sample.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.groupby.DataFrameGroupBy.sample"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.sample.groupby_sample:1 of
msgid "Return a random sample of items from each group."
msgstr "从每个组中返回随机样本项。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.sample.groupby_sample:3 of
msgid "You can use `random_state` for reproducibility."
msgstr "您可以使用 `random_state` 来保证结果的可重现性。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.sample.groupby_sample of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.sample.groupby_sample:5 of
msgid ""
"Number of items to return for each group. Cannot be used with `frac` and "
"must be no larger than the smallest group unless `replace` is True. "
"Default is one if `frac` is None."
msgstr ""
"每组要返回的项数。不能与 `frac` 同时使用，且除非 `replace` 为 True，否则"
"不能超过最小组的大小。如果 `frac` 为 None，则默认值为 1。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.sample.groupby_sample:9 of
msgid "Fraction of items to return. Cannot be used with `n`."
msgstr "要返回的项的比例。不能与 `n` 同时使用。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.sample.groupby_sample:11 of
msgid "Allow or disallow sampling of the same row more than once."
msgstr "允许或不允许对同一行进行多次采样。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.sample.groupby_sample:13 of
msgid ""
"Default None results in equal probability weighting. If passed a list-"
"like then values must have the same length as the underlying DataFrame or"
" Series object and will be used as sampling probabilities after "
"normalization within each group. Values must be non-negative with at "
"least one positive element within each group."
msgstr ""
"默认值 None 表示等概率加权。如果传入一个类列表对象，则其值必须与底层 "
"DataFrame 或 Series 对象具有相同的长度，并将作为每组内归一化后的采样概率"
"。值必须是非负数，并且每组中至少有一个正值元素。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.sample.groupby_sample:20 of
msgid ""
"If int, array-like, or BitGenerator (NumPy>=1.17), seed for random number"
" generator If np.random.RandomState, use as numpy RandomState object."
msgstr ""
"如果为 int、array-like 或 BitGenerator (NumPy>=1.17)，则为随机数生成器的"
"种子；如果为 np.random.RandomState，则用作 numpy RandomState 对象。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.sample.groupby_sample:24 of
msgid ""
"If ignore, errors will not be raised when `replace` is False and size of "
"some group is less than `n`."
msgstr ""
"如果为 ignore，当 `replace` 为 False 且某些组的大小小于 `n` 时将不会引发"
"错误。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.sample.groupby_sample of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.sample.groupby_sample:28 of
msgid ""
"A new object of same type as caller containing items randomly sampled "
"within each group from the caller object."
msgstr "一个与调用者相同类型的新对象，其中包含从调用者对象中每个组内随机采样的项。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.sample.groupby_sample of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.sample.groupby_sample:34 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.sample`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.sample.groupby_sample:35 of
msgid "Generate random samples from a DataFrame object."
msgstr "从 DataFrame 对象中生成随机样本。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.sample.groupby_sample:37 of
msgid ":py:obj:`numpy.random.choice`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.sample.groupby_sample:38 of
msgid "Generate a random sample from a given 1-D numpy array."
msgstr "从给定的一维 numpy 数组中生成随机样本。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.sample.groupby_sample:41 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.sample.groupby_sample:55 of
msgid ""
"Select one row at random for each distinct value in column a. The "
"`random_state` argument can be used to guarantee reproducibility:"
msgstr ""
"为列 a 中的每个不同值随机选择一行。`random_state` 参数可用于保证结果的可"
"重现性："

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.sample.groupby_sample:64 of
msgid "Set `frac` to sample fixed proportions rather than counts:"
msgstr "设置 `frac` 来按固定比例而不是固定数量进行采样："

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.sample.groupby_sample:72 of
msgid "Control sample probabilities within groups by setting weights:"
msgstr "通过设置权重来控制组内的采样概率："

